ActCanadian Race Relations Foundation Act
PrecisAppointment of ANNE-MARIE PHAM of Calgary, Alberta, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Race Relations Foundation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, on a part-time basis, effective December 18, 2017.
